sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant PasswordController
    participant ChangePasswordRequest
    participant UserService
    participant ApiClient
    participant ExternalAPI

    Note over Browser,ExternalAPI: GET /account/password (edit)
    Browser->>PasswordController: GET /account/password
    PasswordController-->>Browser: Inertia::render("account/password")

    Note over Browser,ExternalAPI: PUT /account/password (update)
    Browser->>PasswordController: PUT /account/password {current_password, password, password_confirmation}
    PasswordController->>ChangePasswordRequest: validate()
    ChangePasswordRequest-->>PasswordController: validated data

    PasswordController->>UserService: changePassword(validated)
    UserService->>ApiClient: put("/password", data)
    ApiClient->>ExternalAPI: PUT /api/password
    ExternalAPI-->>ApiClient: 200 {message} | 422 {errors}
    ApiClient-->>UserService: Response
    UserService-->>PasswordController: Response

    alt API returns 200
        PasswordController-->>Browser: redirect back with success flash
    else API returns 422
        PasswordController-->>Browser: redirect back with validation errors
    else Connection failure
        PasswordController-->>Browser: redirect back with connection error
    end
